### Test Business Management API
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get my business
GET {{baseUrl}}/businesses/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Update my business
PUT {{baseUrl}}/businesses/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "businessName": "Test Business Updated",
  "description": "Salon de coiffure moderne",
  "category": "HAIRDRESSER",
  "address": "123 Rue de Paris",
  "city": "Paris",
  "postalCode": "75001"
}

### 3. Get business by slug (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/businesses/test-business

### ====== SERVICES ======

### 4. Create a service
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Coupe Homme",
  "description": "Coupe classique pour homme",
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "price": 25.00,
  "color": "#3B82F6"
}

### 5. List all services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get service by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/services/SERVICE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Update a service
PUT {{baseUrl}}/services/SERVICE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Coupe Homme Premium",
  "description": "Coupe classique avec shampooing",
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "price": 30.00,
  "color": "#3B82F6"
}

### 8. Delete a service (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/services/SERVICE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====== SCHEDULES ======

### 9. Create schedule for Monday
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dayOfWeek": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "18:00:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30
}

### 10. Create schedule for Tuesday
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dayOfWeek": "TUESDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "18:00:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30
}

### 11. Create schedule for Friday (different hours)
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dayOfWeek": "FRIDAY",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30
}

### 12. List all schedules
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Update a schedule
PUT {{baseUrl}}/schedules/SCHEDULE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "dayOfWeek": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "19:00:00",
  "slotDurationMinutes": 30
}

### 14. Delete a schedule (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/schedules/SCHEDULE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
